WEBVTT

00:14.880 --> 00:15.590
Miss Fan.

00:19.390 --> 00:20.480
I agreed.

00:21.000 --> 00:22.510
Well, drink it while it's hot.

00:22.510 --> 00:23.760
I mean,

00:24.670 --> 00:26.000
I agreed to marry into

00:26.670 --> 00:27.760
your family.

00:35.350 --> 00:36.070
Okay.

00:37.640 --> 00:38.350
Good.

00:40.200 --> 00:42.000
After we are married,

00:42.320 --> 00:44.960
we'll tell others
that you married into my family.

00:44.960 --> 00:46.350
Once the house title is transferred

00:46.350 --> 00:47.640
and the money situation is sorted out,

00:47.640 --> 00:50.280
I'll hire the very best doctor in town

00:50.320 --> 00:51.640
and use the finest medicine
to treat your injuries.

00:51.640 --> 00:52.770
After you recover,

00:52.850 --> 00:53.590
whether you want to stay or go

00:53.590 --> 00:54.470
is entirely up to you.

00:54.470 --> 00:57.280
Aren't you afraid that after I leave,

00:58.030 --> 01:00.830
your uncle will come back
to seize the house again?

01:03.200 --> 01:04.379
Once the property is in my name,

01:04.379 --> 01:05.950
why should I be afraid of him?

01:05.950 --> 01:06.920
Besides,

01:07.120 --> 01:08.400
when you leave,

01:08.480 --> 01:10.680
I'll just say you've gone on a long trip.

01:10.740 --> 01:12.140
Who would know the truth?

01:13.600 --> 01:15.260
You've thought this through.

01:17.640 --> 01:18.840
If you decide to stay,

01:19.350 --> 01:21.210
I'll feed you by butchering pigs.

01:22.310 --> 01:23.150
Why?

01:23.590 --> 01:24.789
You may not know this,

01:25.230 --> 01:27.560
but we butchers make a lot of money.

01:29.430 --> 01:30.560
I mean,

01:32.039 --> 01:33.590
if I am a cripple,

01:34.120 --> 01:36.000
what would you gain from keeping me?

01:36.000 --> 01:37.729
Because you're good-looking.

01:38.950 --> 01:40.570
Fan Changyu,

01:40.870 --> 01:41.400
how could you say something

01:41.400 --> 01:43.310
so heartfelt?

01:45.310 --> 01:46.710
There are countless

01:47.039 --> 01:49.039
good-looking people in this world.

01:49.950 --> 01:50.680
Why me?

01:50.789 --> 01:53.400
But the one I carried out of the snow
was you.

01:55.710 --> 01:58.140
If you have nowhere to go
after you recover...

01:58.140 --> 01:59.070
After I recover,

01:59.400 --> 02:01.020
I will leave.

02:02.070 --> 02:03.670
I won't overstay my welcome.

02:10.120 --> 02:11.050
That's fine too.

02:12.750 --> 02:13.820
I'll be going now.

02:17.800 --> 02:18.680
Miss Fan.

02:21.190 --> 02:22.280
I will repay you

02:23.280 --> 02:24.340
for saving my life.

02:24.910 --> 02:26.750
If you have any wish,

02:27.800 --> 02:28.590
just say it.

02:30.630 --> 02:32.690
I don't really have any other wishes.

02:33.870 --> 02:35.150
I'm already very grateful that

02:35.150 --> 02:36.680
you agreed
to pretend to marry into my family

02:36.680 --> 02:38.140
and help me keep the house.

02:38.150 --> 02:39.960
Pretending to marry into your family

02:39.960 --> 02:42.680
is just my way
of repaying your kindness in taking me in.

02:42.680 --> 02:44.590
If you have any wishes,

02:44.870 --> 02:46.079
you can dream big.

02:47.400 --> 02:49.150
Wishes?

02:51.120 --> 02:52.190
Dream big?

02:54.030 --> 02:55.310
Then I'll dream big.

02:56.240 --> 02:58.120
I want to run

02:58.150 --> 02:59.360
my father's pigsty,

02:59.630 --> 03:01.400
get a bigger plot of land,

03:02.000 --> 03:04.030
and keep 20 or 30 pigs.

03:08.470 --> 03:11.840
You can... go bigger.

03:11.840 --> 03:12.960
Then 100 pigs.

03:14.750 --> 03:16.070
I mean,

03:16.870 --> 03:18.840
do you have any grand life goals?

03:19.030 --> 03:22.120
100 pigs are worth
over 100 taels of silver.

03:22.430 --> 03:24.200
Isn't that a grand life goal?

03:24.280 --> 03:24.750
Well...

03:24.750 --> 03:26.079
Then 200 pigs.

03:26.750 --> 03:27.910
200 pigs?

03:27.910 --> 03:29.370
I can't butcher that many.

03:32.150 --> 03:33.030
Got it.

03:36.630 --> 03:38.490
Let's make a pact with a high five.

03:48.020 --> 03:49.310
Hello, Miss Changyu.

03:49.520 --> 03:50.150
Hello.

03:58.870 --> 04:01.120
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

04:01.120 --> 04:03.870
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

04:04.240 --> 04:05.230
Go play.

04:14.590 --> 04:15.150
Here.

04:15.710 --> 04:16.510
Okay.

04:16.870 --> 04:17.700
One, two!

04:17.800 --> 04:18.860
Thank you, miss.

04:21.339 --> 04:22.550
Alright. Here.

04:24.310 --> 04:24.950
Mrs. Wang.

04:24.950 --> 04:25.630
Changyu.

04:25.630 --> 04:26.680
Wang, Zhang.

04:26.860 --> 04:35.590
[Yaxiu Embroidery House]

04:34.920 --> 04:35.870
Ma'am,

04:36.510 --> 04:38.720
my mother had previously reserved fabric

04:38.720 --> 04:40.730
for my wedding clothes at your shop.

04:41.870 --> 04:42.750
Follow me this way.

04:42.750 --> 04:43.190
Okay.

04:49.630 --> 04:51.950
She did reserve a batch of fabric,

04:52.040 --> 04:55.310
just enough
for a full set of wedding clothes.

04:55.800 --> 04:57.830
Can it be made into
a groom's wedding outfit?

04:57.830 --> 04:59.560
A groom's wedding outfit?

05:00.720 --> 05:02.720
I knew that voice sounded familiar.

05:03.000 --> 05:04.920
Isn't this Changyu?

05:04.920 --> 05:05.970
Mrs. Chen.

05:06.310 --> 05:07.640
I heard from Mrs. Zhao

05:07.670 --> 05:09.750
that your family
is joining the wedding frenzy.

05:09.750 --> 05:11.650
When is the big day?

05:11.750 --> 05:12.720
In 7 days.

05:13.270 --> 05:14.950
Then it might be too late

05:14.950 --> 05:16.410
to order wedding clothes.

05:16.600 --> 05:18.510
Upon hearing that the army
is recruiting in Chongzhou,

05:18.510 --> 05:20.430
everyone is rushing

05:20.870 --> 05:22.720
to get married to secure an heir.

05:23.240 --> 05:24.430
My staff in the shop

05:24.430 --> 05:25.490
can barely keep up.

05:28.510 --> 05:29.940
I heard from Mrs. Zhao

05:29.970 --> 05:31.900
that your groom is quite handsome.

05:32.950 --> 05:34.280
I suppose so.

05:34.430 --> 05:35.830
Anyway, I'm not at a loss.

05:36.510 --> 05:38.720
Mrs. Chen, please speed up the work.

05:38.830 --> 05:40.480
I'll pay you extra.

05:40.510 --> 05:42.180
Who's asking for that?

05:42.390 --> 05:43.670
Don't worry.

05:43.720 --> 05:44.630
I helped your mother

05:44.630 --> 05:47.110
pick out this fabric for the wedding clothes
and left it here.

05:47.110 --> 05:49.370
She was looking forward to your wedding.

05:52.560 --> 05:54.000
I heard from Mrs. Zhao that the groom

05:54.000 --> 05:57.510
is her distant relative from Chongzhou.

06:03.190 --> 06:05.000
From Chongzhou?

06:05.630 --> 06:08.830
Does he know whether the Marquis of Wu'an
is alive or dead?

06:09.630 --> 06:11.430
Th-The Marquis of Wu'an is dead?

06:11.600 --> 06:12.430
Is that true?

06:12.430 --> 06:13.630
The Marquis of Wu'an?

06:13.870 --> 06:17.110
-Listen. Isn't that what people say?
-The Marquis of Wu'an really died.

06:17.110 --> 06:17.920
He died in Chongzhou.

06:17.920 --> 06:18.630
No remains were found.

06:18.630 --> 06:19.830
Just like his father.

06:20.120 --> 06:20.950
Nonsense!

06:20.950 --> 06:22.430
How could the Marquis of Wu'an be dead?

06:22.430 --> 06:23.630
I'll slap you!

06:23.630 --> 06:25.760
Don't you think he deserves a beating?

06:38.350 --> 06:43.670
[Chongde Hall]

06:39.870 --> 06:41.100
Our Great Yin

06:41.270 --> 06:43.770
has been at war with Beijue for years.

06:44.159 --> 06:47.070
Xie Zheng, the Marquis of Wu'an,
a hero of his generation,

06:47.070 --> 06:48.920
ended up with no body to bury.

06:49.159 --> 06:51.110
It is truly a tragedy for Great Yin.

06:52.190 --> 06:52.870
I intend

06:52.530 --> 06:58.450
[Qi Sheng, Emperor of Great Yin]

06:53.630 --> 06:56.700
to posthumously grant Xie Zheng
the title of the Duke of Loyal

06:56.700 --> 06:59.360
and reward the Xie Army
with 1,000 taels of gold.

06:59.950 --> 07:02.510
Ministers, what do you think?

07:07.270 --> 07:09.070
Your Majesty, your wisdom shines.

07:09.070 --> 07:11.720
The Marquis of Wu'an
defended the northwest

07:11.720 --> 07:13.010
with unmatched bravery.

07:13.010 --> 07:15.130
In the hundred-plus years
of the Great Yin dynasty,

07:13.150 --> 07:17.450
[Li Jing, Grand Tutor of Great Yin]

07:15.300 --> 07:17.220
only Xie Zheng

07:17.620 --> 07:19.440
was truly worthy of such a title.

07:19.600 --> 07:22.690
Granting him the title
of Duke of Loyal posthumously now

07:22.690 --> 07:25.400
demonstrates your virtue.

07:25.430 --> 07:27.530
It is a blessing for the people.

07:27.870 --> 07:30.340
In his youth,
Xie Zheng, the Marquis of Wu'an,

07:30.340 --> 07:33.080
led troops to avenge
the humiliation at Jinzhou.

07:33.270 --> 07:36.210
The Beijue people
tremble at the mention of his name.

07:36.240 --> 07:38.810
All officers and soldiers
will gladly give their lives

07:38.730 --> 07:43.450
[Diligent and Virtuous]

07:38.840 --> 07:40.800
to repay Your Majesty's grace.

07:40.800 --> 07:42.120
We second the motion.

07:42.580 --> 07:44.950
Very well. Convey my decree.

07:45.340 --> 07:46.510
In my grief,

07:46.530 --> 07:48.050
I shall suspend court for 3 days

07:48.050 --> 07:49.340
and wear plain robes to mourn.

07:49.340 --> 07:51.900
The whole realm shall mourn deeply.

07:52.340 --> 07:54.730
Yes, Your Majesty.

07:55.100 --> 07:57.610
Your Majesty, I am late.

08:22.770 --> 08:24.790
Prime Minister, despite your ill health,

08:24.790 --> 08:26.120
you still came to court.

08:26.620 --> 08:28.350
This is a blessing to Great Yin.

08:29.290 --> 08:30.220
Grant him a seat.

08:37.659 --> 08:41.320
[Wei Yan, Prime Minister of Great Yin]

08:39.250 --> 08:40.620
Where were we?

08:42.110 --> 08:45.500
I intend to posthumously grant Xie Zheng
the title of the Duke of Loyal,

08:45.500 --> 08:47.440
reward the Xie Army
with 1,000 taels of gold,

08:47.440 --> 08:48.900
and have the nation mourn.

08:50.460 --> 08:52.590
Prime Minister Wei, what is your view?

08:54.820 --> 08:57.370
Though the Marquis of Wu'an
had military merit,

08:57.370 --> 09:00.100
this matter concerns
the front-line situation.

09:00.690 --> 09:02.810
If the entire nation mourns,

09:03.390 --> 09:06.230
I fear it may dampen the army's morale.

09:06.310 --> 09:07.140
At that time,

09:07.170 --> 09:10.160
the enemy forces of Beijue
and Prince Changxin

09:10.620 --> 09:12.770
may seize the opportunity to strike.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.450
Prime Minister Wei,

09:21.920 --> 09:25.300
the Marquis of Wu'an died young
in service to the state.

09:25.580 --> 09:28.580
His Majesty's action
is out of pity for his early death

09:29.160 --> 09:31.710
and reflects his benevolent intent.

09:32.610 --> 09:36.420
Though scholars often criticize

09:36.420 --> 09:37.880
his slaughter at Jinzhou,

09:38.260 --> 09:40.160
when merits and faults are weighed,

09:40.160 --> 09:42.370
his merits far outweigh his faults.

09:43.260 --> 09:45.420
Rewarding the Marquis of Wu'an now

09:45.450 --> 09:47.530
is a clear act
of just reward and punishment

09:47.530 --> 09:49.550
and a strategy that lifts morale.

09:50.100 --> 09:53.610
Why would it weaken the army?

09:55.620 --> 09:58.250
It has been said
that the Marquis of Wu'an fell in battle,

09:58.250 --> 10:00.610
yet his body
hasn't been found to this day.

10:00.910 --> 10:02.700
I have kept the news undisclosed

10:02.700 --> 10:04.870
to mislead the enemy.

10:05.690 --> 10:08.420
As long as his death
is not officially announced,

10:08.770 --> 10:11.130
the enemy will not know the truth

10:11.860 --> 10:13.950
and will not dare to advance rashly.

10:15.130 --> 10:19.360
Grand Tutor, though you are skilled
at discerning His Majesty's intent,

10:20.090 --> 10:22.420
you must still apply yourself diligently

10:22.770 --> 10:25.730
to military strategy.

10:36.520 --> 10:38.810
Prime Minister Wei, you're thoughtful.

10:39.930 --> 10:42.980
Thank you for your guidance.

10:44.260 --> 10:45.450
Prime Minister Wei.

10:51.760 --> 10:54.110
My condolences.

10:55.230 --> 10:57.030
That is kind of you, Grand Tutor.

10:58.580 --> 11:01.770
Now that the Marquis of Wu'an
is not guarding Yanzhou,

11:02.760 --> 11:04.280
who else

11:04.300 --> 11:06.390
can control the Yanzhou Army?

11:09.590 --> 11:13.190
The Yanzhou Army is also Great Yin's army.

11:13.370 --> 11:15.100
Any capable people in the court

11:15.180 --> 11:17.150
can go to Yanzhou.

11:17.920 --> 11:20.880
The Yanzhou Army
concerns the safety of the border.

11:21.160 --> 11:22.910
We must be cautious.

11:27.100 --> 11:29.370
You have a foolproof plan.

11:29.400 --> 11:31.050
I was worrying too much.

11:32.400 --> 11:33.160
Farewell.

11:43.310 --> 11:46.070
This old fox cares so much about
the situation in the Northwest.

11:46.070 --> 11:49.270
I'm afraid he wants to meddle
in border military affairs.

11:53.740 --> 11:55.780
Has Xie Zheng's body been found?

11:55.930 --> 11:56.760
Not yet.

11:59.110 --> 12:00.770
Regarding the Marquis of Wu'an's
disappearance,

12:00.770 --> 12:03.390
has the Eldest Young Master sent word?

12:04.220 --> 12:04.820
No.

12:05.430 --> 12:08.430
We were too close
to He Jingyuan's territory that day.

12:08.930 --> 12:10.590
We feared alerting the enemy.

12:11.700 --> 12:14.360
I have sent men
to continue the search in secret.

12:14.420 --> 12:15.400
Keep searching.

12:15.790 --> 12:16.820
Tell him to hurry.

12:16.850 --> 12:17.370
Yes.

12:17.850 --> 12:20.850
We must confirm he's dead or alive.

12:20.890 --> 12:23.540
But the key is finding that token.

12:23.540 --> 12:23.970
Yes.

12:24.100 --> 12:25.960
Tell the people of the Black Cross

12:26.630 --> 12:27.590
not to come back

12:28.610 --> 12:29.800
if they can't find it.

12:29.800 --> 12:30.680
Yes.

13:55.810 --> 14:01.050
[Pursuit of Jade]

14:01.140 --> 14:03.870
[Episode 3]

14:05.040 --> 14:05.730
Go away!

14:07.250 --> 14:08.090
Get lost!

14:08.860 --> 14:09.650
Go away!

14:10.770 --> 14:11.690
Go away!

14:11.710 --> 14:12.420
Go away!

14:12.610 --> 14:13.470
Go away!

14:16.250 --> 14:16.970
Go away!

14:17.000 --> 14:17.720
Go away!

14:19.100 --> 14:19.980
Go away!

14:23.870 --> 14:25.670
Where did that wild wolf come from?

14:25.670 --> 14:27.330
It nearly took my hair ribbon.

14:31.770 --> 14:32.700
Where is my shoe?

15:02.890 --> 15:05.420
This young lady
really doesn't fear the cold.

15:05.610 --> 15:06.900
It's snowing heavily,

15:06.920 --> 15:08.590
yet she's walking barefoot.

15:22.420 --> 15:24.510
She must have met with some trouble
on the road.

15:24.510 --> 15:25.720
Ask where she lives.

15:25.750 --> 15:26.950
We'll give her a ride.

15:28.260 --> 15:29.110
Miss.

15:32.180 --> 15:34.420
My master can't bear to see you
struggling in the snow

15:34.420 --> 15:35.550
and offers you a ride.

15:35.550 --> 15:36.550
Where do you live?

15:37.940 --> 15:39.460
No need. Thank you.

15:42.790 --> 15:43.850
Miss, please wait.

15:56.220 --> 15:57.080
My surname is Li.

15:57.080 --> 15:58.210
I'm not a bad person.

15:58.740 --> 15:59.970
Walking barefoot in this weather,

15:59.970 --> 16:01.320
your feet will be ruined.

16:01.320 --> 16:02.520
Let me give you a ride.

16:07.460 --> 16:08.820
Well, thank you, sir.

16:18.250 --> 16:19.460
Thank you, sir.

16:34.100 --> 16:35.760
But with you sitting outside,

16:35.900 --> 16:37.350
I feel bad.

16:38.000 --> 16:38.720
It's fine.

16:38.890 --> 16:40.020
Miss, your shoes and socks are soaked.

16:40.020 --> 16:40.830
Dry them off.

16:41.480 --> 16:43.060
I was getting stuffy in the carriage.

16:43.060 --> 16:44.320
I came out for some air.

16:57.050 --> 16:59.450
Changyu, you're back so early.

16:59.940 --> 17:00.940
Changyu.

17:01.470 --> 17:03.300
What... what happened to you?

17:04.849 --> 17:06.339
I met a wild wolf on the way

17:06.560 --> 17:08.160
and lost a shoe running away.

17:08.300 --> 17:10.560
Thanks to these two gentlemen
for bringing me back.

17:10.560 --> 17:11.420
It was nothing.

17:12.329 --> 17:13.900
Thank you, gentlemen.

17:14.540 --> 17:15.780
It's freezing.

17:15.780 --> 17:17.020
Come in and warm up.

17:17.020 --> 17:17.609
Ma'am,

17:17.940 --> 17:19.940
let Miss Fan change her shoes first.

17:19.940 --> 17:21.210
We have urgent matters.

17:21.210 --> 17:22.410
We'll take our leave.

17:22.810 --> 17:24.010
Thank you, Mr. Li.

17:26.890 --> 17:28.290
Sorry for the intrusion.

17:28.480 --> 17:29.480
Please wait.

17:29.650 --> 17:31.670
Here are some freshly roasted chestnuts.

17:31.670 --> 17:33.280
Take them for the road.

17:33.300 --> 17:33.870
No need.

17:33.890 --> 17:36.480
My auntie roasts delicious chestnuts.

17:36.500 --> 17:37.830
Yes, they taste great.

17:37.980 --> 17:39.170
Please try some.

17:39.200 --> 17:40.430
It would be impolite to refuse.

17:40.430 --> 17:41.430
Thank you, ma'am.

17:41.780 --> 17:43.510
-Okay. Wait a minute.
-M'am...

17:45.810 --> 17:46.880
Why did you say yes?

17:46.960 --> 17:48.570
The villagers' way of showing gratitude

17:48.570 --> 17:49.610
is just this simple.

17:49.610 --> 17:51.460
We need to blend in with them.

17:52.000 --> 17:53.930
It helps with your investigation.

17:53.930 --> 17:54.540
Right?

17:55.630 --> 17:57.720
Just admit you're craving them.

18:15.980 --> 18:17.390
I didn't see anything.

18:21.870 --> 18:22.520
Come in.

18:29.300 --> 18:30.130
I... I...

18:30.210 --> 18:34.170
I went to Mrs. Chen's
to tailor the wedding clothes today

18:34.170 --> 18:36.230
and realized I forgot to measure you.

18:38.550 --> 18:39.310
Come on in.

19:05.340 --> 19:07.190
You look thin,

19:08.130 --> 19:10.130
but your shoulders are quite broad.

19:10.860 --> 19:11.990
Just like my father.

19:12.660 --> 19:14.100
Shoulder width, 1.8 chi.

19:28.060 --> 19:29.410
Waist, 2.1 chi.

19:32.050 --> 19:33.810
Legs, 3.7 chi.

19:37.240 --> 19:38.040
What's wrong?

19:39.060 --> 19:39.980
Nothing.

19:40.210 --> 19:41.790
I was chased by a wolf this morning.

19:41.790 --> 19:43.520
I might have sprained my ankle.

19:44.170 --> 19:45.520
Sit down. Let me check.

19:45.550 --> 19:46.310
No need.

19:47.220 --> 19:49.060
Mr. Zhao will be back soon.

19:49.210 --> 19:50.940
I'll just apply some medicine.

19:56.610 --> 19:57.650
Sit down.

19:57.870 --> 19:58.760
Let me take a look.

19:58.760 --> 20:00.420
Or it will hurt again tonight.

20:03.130 --> 20:03.930
Is it good?

20:03.930 --> 20:04.930
Yes.

20:12.670 --> 20:13.600
I don't know why,

20:14.340 --> 20:17.400
but those mysterious people retreated
at Lin'an Town.

20:22.300 --> 20:24.050
They vanished completely.

20:24.900 --> 20:25.750
Should I

20:25.940 --> 20:28.210
ask the local magistrate of Lin'an?

20:30.080 --> 20:31.280
My mentor said

20:31.540 --> 20:33.340
this matter must be kept secret.

20:39.690 --> 20:40.320
My Lord,

20:40.640 --> 20:41.980
you've been searching
for the Marquis of Wu'an

20:41.980 --> 20:43.260
night after night,

20:43.490 --> 20:44.890
but we still have no news.

20:45.340 --> 20:46.310
If you ask me,

20:46.740 --> 20:48.000
in the chaos of war,

20:48.020 --> 20:49.680
disappearing without a trace

20:49.850 --> 20:50.980
is nothing new.

20:51.370 --> 20:52.370
I feel like

20:53.780 --> 20:56.240
the Marquis of Wu'an
wouldn't die so easily.

20:58.450 --> 21:00.850
If those mysterious people are lingering,

21:01.760 --> 21:04.160
the Marquis of Wu'an
must be in Lin'an Town.

21:10.060 --> 21:11.060
It's dislocated.

21:12.820 --> 21:13.620
It hurts!

21:13.650 --> 21:15.310
Of course a dislocation hurts.

21:15.310 --> 21:17.490
I thought it was just a sprain.

21:18.620 --> 21:19.490
Bear with it.

21:24.170 --> 21:25.030
Done.

21:34.600 --> 21:35.730
My Lords,

21:36.280 --> 21:37.810
freshly roasted chestnuts.

21:37.810 --> 21:38.850
They are still warm.

21:38.850 --> 21:39.850
Eat them while they're hot.

21:39.850 --> 21:40.690
Thank you, ma'am.

21:40.690 --> 21:41.210
Ma'am,

21:42.190 --> 21:43.050
I just heard

21:43.070 --> 21:44.830
Miss Fan screaming in the attic.

21:44.830 --> 21:45.960
Is something wrong?

21:46.510 --> 21:48.750
That is Changyu's husband.

21:49.160 --> 21:51.260
The young couple
is probably just playing around.

21:51.260 --> 21:52.110
Husband?

21:54.210 --> 21:57.030
Why didn't he come down
to welcome Miss Fan just now?

21:57.030 --> 21:58.190
He has an injury.

21:58.220 --> 21:59.680
He can't come down easily.

22:01.560 --> 22:02.210
Is it good?

22:02.230 --> 22:03.640
It's delicious, ma'am.

22:04.150 --> 22:06.010
The Northwest is at war right now.

22:06.220 --> 22:07.500
I heard many injured refugees
from Chongzhou

22:07.500 --> 22:09.320
came here,

22:09.350 --> 22:11.150
hoping to marry and settle down.

22:11.260 --> 22:12.600
Is Miss Fan's husband

22:13.170 --> 22:14.630
from Chongzhou too?

22:18.820 --> 22:20.830
He is a distant relative of mine

22:20.850 --> 22:22.100
from Yanzhou.

22:23.000 --> 22:23.960
Yanzhou?

22:29.390 --> 22:30.960
It's really healed.

22:31.540 --> 22:32.800
It doesn't hurt at all.

22:37.340 --> 22:38.740
I told you not to wolf it down.

22:38.740 --> 22:40.020
You choked, didn't you?

22:40.020 --> 22:40.580
Ma'am,

22:40.910 --> 22:42.210
may we have some tea?

22:42.240 --> 22:43.230
Sure.

22:43.910 --> 22:45.400
I was so focused on the food

22:45.420 --> 22:46.440
and forgot the drinks.

22:46.440 --> 22:46.960
Come.

22:47.030 --> 22:47.980
Come in and have some tea.

22:47.980 --> 22:48.580
Thank you.

22:56.060 --> 22:57.390
Is someone downstairs?

22:58.110 --> 22:58.760
Oh no.

22:59.210 --> 23:01.210
I forgot my two saviors downstairs.

23:06.170 --> 23:08.280
Please excuse the poor tea.

23:09.090 --> 23:11.220
Mrs. Fan, did you just get married?

23:14.290 --> 23:15.220
Actually,

23:16.060 --> 23:17.540
he married into my family.

23:18.650 --> 23:20.250
He married into your family?

23:20.660 --> 23:22.660
He's a poor child.

23:22.690 --> 23:25.170
He just came to Lin'an from Yanzhou

23:25.340 --> 23:26.400
and ran into bandits

23:26.400 --> 23:27.250
who robbed

23:27.270 --> 23:28.340
and injured him.

23:28.950 --> 23:31.370
Luckily, our Zhangyu took him in.

23:31.400 --> 23:32.690
She even butchered a pig

23:32.690 --> 23:34.690
and sold it to pay for his treatment.

23:35.310 --> 23:36.290
Butchered a pig?

23:38.430 --> 23:40.340
My sister is amazing.

23:41.050 --> 23:43.240
She can knock out a pig with one slap.

23:44.070 --> 23:45.650
She's kidding.

23:50.780 --> 23:52.280
Mrs. Fan, you're truly virtuous.

23:52.280 --> 23:53.450
Truly virtuous.

23:58.280 --> 23:59.940
Mrs. Fan, no need to see us off.

24:00.410 --> 24:01.000
Here.

24:02.780 --> 24:03.690
Take care.

24:08.260 --> 24:08.890
My Lord.

24:09.700 --> 24:11.320
I think we have lost our minds
trying to find

24:11.320 --> 24:12.580
the Marquis of Wu'an.

24:12.760 --> 24:14.300
He's the kind of man who even refused

24:14.300 --> 24:15.370
a princess.

24:15.550 --> 24:17.740
How could he possibly
marry a butcher girl,

24:17.740 --> 24:20.400
giving her foot massages
and setting her bones?

24:20.570 --> 24:21.930
I overthought it.

24:22.180 --> 24:24.430
You haven't slept in days because of this.

24:24.430 --> 24:26.640
Have a good sleep
on the way back to Jizhou.

24:26.640 --> 24:28.240
I'll handle things outside.

24:29.040 --> 24:29.660
Let's go.

24:44.560 --> 24:46.120
A carriage from Jizhou?

24:46.690 --> 24:48.220
They're He Jingyuan's men.

24:54.590 --> 24:56.990
What were Yan Zheng's measurements again?

25:06.740 --> 25:08.100
Shoulder width...

25:11.200 --> 25:12.640
1.8 chi.

25:13.630 --> 25:16.770
Waist... 2.1 chi.

25:15.060 --> 25:17.310
[1.8 chi] [2.1 chi]

25:18.990 --> 25:20.220
Legs...

25:20.030 --> 25:22.750
[1.8 chi] [2.1 chi] [3.7 chi]

25:21.180 --> 25:22.310
3.7 chi.

25:33.300 --> 25:34.930
Yan Zheng.

25:36.710 --> 25:37.850
Yan Zheng?

25:43.730 --> 25:46.210
[Xie]

25:50.090 --> 25:52.380
[Xie Zheng]

25:55.020 --> 26:01.000
[Xie Zheng]

26:04.230 --> 26:05.380
This is...

26:06.340 --> 26:07.930
Did she discover something?

26:07.170 --> 26:09.150
[Xie Zheng]

26:20.100 --> 26:20.740
Who is it?

26:21.850 --> 26:22.650
It's me.

26:23.360 --> 26:24.960
I have something to tell you.

26:28.610 --> 26:29.260
Come in.

26:44.900 --> 26:46.820
I've noted the measurements.

26:47.600 --> 26:49.130
I'll send them over in a bit.

27:01.050 --> 27:03.430
Can you stay up tonight?

27:03.870 --> 27:05.800
Wait for me. I have something to do.

27:08.940 --> 27:11.520
It can only be done if we do it together.

27:17.940 --> 27:19.300
Together?

27:19.600 --> 27:21.200
You're a man, and I'm a woman.

27:21.460 --> 27:23.130
I can't do it without you.

27:34.700 --> 27:36.630
That wouldn't be proper, would it?

27:37.140 --> 27:38.370
You'll be my matrilocal husband soon.

27:38.370 --> 27:39.830
What's improper about it?

27:40.100 --> 27:41.160
It's settled then.

27:51.550 --> 27:53.880
Don't let Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao
know about this.

27:53.880 --> 27:54.810
Keep it a secret.

28:37.060 --> 28:38.460
What do you want me to do?

28:38.580 --> 28:40.580
Don't let anyone see you. Follow me.

28:50.010 --> 28:50.860
Kneel.

28:59.520 --> 29:01.330
This is the thing

29:02.030 --> 29:03.690
you said we had to do together?

29:06.130 --> 29:07.190
My mother said that

29:07.440 --> 29:10.170
when visiting a grave at midnight,
you need a man,

29:10.930 --> 29:12.590
a man with strong yang energy.

29:12.860 --> 29:13.760
That's you.

29:14.100 --> 29:16.830
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

29:19.560 --> 29:21.750
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

29:21.770 --> 29:24.790
[Xie Zheng]

29:28.610 --> 29:29.930
So that's why she was writing that

29:29.930 --> 29:32.020
in the sand earlier today.

29:33.940 --> 29:35.890
The authorities
haven't issued an obituary.

29:35.890 --> 29:38.930
I was afraid that private mourning
could get us in trouble.

29:38.930 --> 29:41.450
It's best to do it at midnight
when no one's around.

29:41.450 --> 29:42.910
And this memorial tablet?

29:46.140 --> 29:48.090
You were coughing up blood badly
back then.

29:48.090 --> 29:49.820
I thought you wouldn't make it,

29:50.540 --> 29:51.940
so I had it carved for you.

29:53.920 --> 29:54.910
Thank you.

29:55.320 --> 29:57.650
Don't mention it. We didn't use it anyway.

30:00.220 --> 30:02.420
The Marquis of Wu'an has died in battle.

30:02.810 --> 30:05.130
I wanted to set up a memorial tablet
for him.

30:05.130 --> 30:06.100
Surprisingly,

30:06.370 --> 30:08.900
a small change to your name
could make it work.

30:09.740 --> 30:10.500
Yeah.

30:11.240 --> 30:12.900
It works out perfectly for me.

30:14.170 --> 30:15.280
It's yellow rosewood.

30:15.280 --> 30:16.810
It'd be a waste not to use it.

30:18.100 --> 30:18.770
By the way,

30:18.800 --> 30:21.130
you came here as a refugee from Chongzhou.

30:21.330 --> 30:23.590
Do you know how the Marquis of Wu'an died?

30:24.550 --> 30:25.160
I don't.

30:29.040 --> 30:31.440
You're not related
to the Marquis of Wu'an.

30:31.900 --> 30:33.900
Why set up a memorial tablet for him?

30:34.260 --> 30:35.700
Doesn't everyone say

30:36.220 --> 30:38.580
that the Marquis of Wu'an
is a bloodthirsty,

30:38.580 --> 30:40.690
violent living Yama
who slaughtered a city?

30:40.690 --> 30:41.540
Nonsense!

30:42.890 --> 30:43.820
My father said

30:44.520 --> 30:45.760
he led the army

30:46.220 --> 30:48.180
and took back Jinzhou from Beijue,

30:48.780 --> 30:49.910
avenging his father

30:51.130 --> 30:52.450
and Great Yin.

30:53.540 --> 30:54.740
As for the slaughter—

30:55.780 --> 30:57.110
if the enemy could do it,

30:58.130 --> 30:59.370
why couldn't he?

31:08.100 --> 31:09.360
Do you really think so?

31:11.020 --> 31:12.920
My father often told me

31:13.040 --> 31:14.970
that in over 200 years of Great Yin,

31:15.040 --> 31:17.300
there has been only one Marquis of Wu'an.

31:17.720 --> 31:19.380
Jinzhou was reclaimed by him.

31:21.260 --> 31:23.060
The 12 prefectures of Liaodong,

31:23.450 --> 31:25.300
which had suffered the loss
of countless loyal ministers

31:25.300 --> 31:26.980
and distinguished generals
in decades of war,

31:26.980 --> 31:28.510
were also taken back by him.

31:29.560 --> 31:31.280
The scholars of our time

31:33.100 --> 31:34.530
all despise what he did.

31:35.610 --> 31:36.850
Those scholars

31:37.340 --> 31:39.200
say he is cold-blooded and cruel.

31:39.630 --> 31:41.600
But what about the soldiers and civilians

31:41.600 --> 31:43.970
who died in Jinzhou 16 years ago?

31:44.190 --> 31:45.660
Were they not innocent?

31:46.170 --> 31:47.840
Old General Xie died standing tall

31:47.840 --> 31:49.230
to maintain his dignity,

31:49.230 --> 31:51.230
but the Beijue people disemboweled him

31:51.230 --> 31:52.610
and displayed his body on the city wall.

31:52.610 --> 31:54.670
He was the Marquis of Wu'an's father.

31:57.910 --> 32:00.490
It is only right to avenge one's father.

32:00.840 --> 32:02.460
Without the Marquis of Wu'an,

32:02.460 --> 32:03.830
who else

32:04.210 --> 32:05.900
could hold the northwest?

32:10.760 --> 32:12.670
Why are you looking at me like that?

32:12.670 --> 32:13.770
Am I wrong?

32:16.370 --> 32:18.170
You really dare to say anything.

32:20.230 --> 32:30.130
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

32:21.880 --> 32:23.280
There's no one else here.

32:23.520 --> 32:25.050
That's why I dared to say it.

32:30.940 --> 32:40.530
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

32:36.330 --> 32:37.570
Marquis of Wu'an,

32:38.240 --> 32:39.760
I, Fan Changyu,

32:40.310 --> 32:41.570
together with my husband, Yan Zheng,

32:41.570 --> 32:42.840
have come to see you off.

32:41.570 --> 32:46.270
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

32:46.290 --> 32:51.190
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

32:46.430 --> 32:48.140
May your spirit in heaven

32:48.580 --> 32:51.440
bless the people of Great Yin
with peace and safety.

32:51.830 --> 32:53.950
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

32:52.940 --> 32:54.600
If you happen to meet my parents,

32:54.540 --> 32:57.250
♪ I find her there ♪

32:57.870 --> 33:03.810
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

32:58.150 --> 32:59.890
please send them my regards.

33:10.470 --> 33:11.900
If you have any wishes,

33:12.330 --> 33:14.190
kneel down, kowtow, and tell him.

33:16.400 --> 33:18.500
The Marquis of Wu'an died for our country.

33:18.500 --> 33:20.700
You'll lose nothing by kneeling to him.

33:22.070 --> 33:26.650
♪ In the east wind,
flowers bloom at night ♪

33:27.680 --> 33:30.680
♪ Blowing down the stars like rain ♪

33:33.060 --> 33:35.330
♪ Fine horses and carved carriages
fill the fragrant streets ♪

33:35.710 --> 33:37.620
♪ The phoenix flute resounds ♪

33:38.230 --> 33:39.490
♪ The jade pot light revolves ♪

33:39.780 --> 33:43.430
♪ A night of fish-and-dragon dances ♪

33:41.920 --> 33:46.760
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

33:43.700 --> 33:48.300
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

33:44.180 --> 33:46.350
May the fog clear soon.

33:47.890 --> 33:49.330
May the truth

33:48.320 --> 33:53.320
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

33:50.580 --> 33:52.380
be revealed to all.

33:53.880 --> 33:56.010
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

33:56.620 --> 34:01.110
♪ I find her there ♪

34:02.710 --> 34:12.219
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

34:18.830 --> 34:25.179
[Xigu Lane]

34:35.219 --> 34:37.100
Changyu.

34:38.190 --> 34:39.590
Changyu.

34:40.710 --> 34:42.880
My braid is crooked.

34:42.900 --> 34:44.260
Come here and let me see.

34:45.469 --> 34:46.790
I'm here.

34:51.350 --> 34:51.949
Come.

34:55.500 --> 34:56.650
It's not crooked.

34:59.170 --> 35:00.650
Just make do with it for today.

35:00.650 --> 35:01.770
When I finish selling the pork,

35:01.770 --> 35:03.430
I'll buy you some candy, okay?

35:04.190 --> 35:05.050
Go get dressed.

35:06.530 --> 35:07.560
Be careful.

35:16.780 --> 35:17.650
Morning, Changyu.

35:17.650 --> 35:18.380
Morning.

35:18.410 --> 35:19.520
Going to work, Changyu?

35:19.520 --> 35:20.850
Morning, ma'am.

35:22.380 --> 35:23.370
Morning, Changyu.

35:23.370 --> 35:24.060
Morning.

35:24.250 --> 35:24.900
Morning.

35:24.930 --> 35:25.520
Morning.

35:25.950 --> 35:26.440
Changyu.

35:26.440 --> 35:26.990
Morning.

35:27.020 --> 35:27.980
Morning, Changyu.

35:27.980 --> 35:28.870
Morning.

35:40.350 --> 35:44.040
[Meat]

35:42.940 --> 35:43.990
Changyu,

35:44.370 --> 35:47.100
are you giving away
the braised pig hearts today?

35:47.230 --> 35:48.330
Not today.

35:48.350 --> 35:50.280
These braised pig hearts are for sale.

35:50.280 --> 35:52.270
I only gave them away on opening day.

35:52.270 --> 35:54.020
I won't be giving them away anymore.

35:54.020 --> 35:55.330
If you want some,

35:55.360 --> 35:56.880
it's 30 mace a jin.

35:58.080 --> 36:01.540
Others give braised offal for free
when you buy meat.

36:01.560 --> 36:03.380
Why do you charge for it?

36:03.540 --> 36:04.580
Which place?

36:05.660 --> 36:06.920
Butcher Guo

36:07.030 --> 36:08.880
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

36:07.080 --> 36:08.970
gives away braised offal
with meat purchases.

36:08.970 --> 36:10.970
Buy meat and get free braised offal!

36:13.780 --> 36:14.550
Come!

36:14.580 --> 36:16.580
Buy meat and get free braised offal!

36:17.330 --> 36:18.610
Are you giving it away or not?

36:18.610 --> 36:20.830
If not, I'm going to his shop.

36:22.770 --> 36:24.280
Yes, of course I am.

36:24.100 --> 36:28.010
[Meat]

36:24.900 --> 36:26.320
Then I won't go to his place.

36:26.320 --> 36:28.050
I'd like 2 jin of pork shoulder.

36:30.850 --> 36:32.380
Mrs. Tao, here's your meat.

36:33.500 --> 36:35.380
Here is your braised pig heart. Take it.

36:35.380 --> 36:36.020
Great.

36:36.130 --> 36:39.380
[Meat]

36:41.170 --> 36:42.250
Here, young lady.

36:42.650 --> 36:43.480
Here's your meat.

36:43.480 --> 36:43.980
Okay.

36:44.280 --> 36:46.070
That Guo is full of tricks.

36:46.240 --> 36:47.690
He wouldn't let you give extras,

36:47.690 --> 36:49.490
but he started doing it himself.

36:50.330 --> 36:52.600
He has an uncle who is an advisor
at the county government office.

36:52.600 --> 36:53.830
Be careful.

36:54.910 --> 36:55.580
Got it.

36:55.830 --> 36:56.820
Look how good this meat is.

36:56.820 --> 36:58.050
Let's go to Fan's.

36:58.070 --> 36:59.350
The lean meat is redder there,

36:59.350 --> 37:00.410
and the braised food smells good.

37:00.410 --> 37:01.950
Unlike the pork here.
It doesn't smell fresh.

37:01.950 --> 37:06.540
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

37:02.080 --> 37:04.310
Hey, what do you mean by that?

37:04.700 --> 37:06.900
Is their brine made of liquid gold?

37:07.750 --> 37:09.390
Good thing you're back.

37:11.050 --> 37:13.880
Let's see how long he can keep giving

37:14.170 --> 37:16.170
the offal boiled in salt water away.

37:16.910 --> 37:18.520
Talking about me, huh?

37:18.610 --> 37:19.100
Fine.

37:20.050 --> 37:22.580
Just you wait.

37:23.610 --> 37:25.870
Mrs. Yin, where are my noodles?

37:25.900 --> 37:26.940
What's the rush?

37:26.960 --> 37:27.990
Like a starving ghost.

37:27.990 --> 37:28.700
I'm coming.

37:28.720 --> 37:29.800
I am hungry.

37:30.860 --> 37:31.670
Hurry up.

37:32.440 --> 37:33.110
Changyu,

37:33.130 --> 37:34.280
I'm going back first.

37:34.280 --> 37:36.020
If that Guo dares to bully you again,

37:36.020 --> 37:36.940
just tell me.

37:37.090 --> 37:38.120
I'm not afraid of him.

37:38.120 --> 37:39.720
I'm not afraid of him either.

37:40.420 --> 37:41.130
I'm off.

37:41.930 --> 37:46.230
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

37:42.060 --> 37:43.280
How many jin of meat do you want?

37:43.280 --> 37:44.140
Two would be fine.

37:44.140 --> 37:45.470
-Two jin, right?
-Two jin for me, too.

37:45.470 --> 37:46.070
Okay.

38:22.610 --> 38:23.380
Stupid bird.

38:23.600 --> 38:25.330
Falling for such a crude trap.

38:35.500 --> 38:36.130
Come up.

38:47.900 --> 38:48.540
Go on.

38:55.990 --> 38:58.990
[Wuqi has arrived at
Four Seasons Bookshop in Lin'an]

39:06.840 --> 39:07.430
Hurry up.

39:08.540 --> 39:09.480
Listen to me.

39:09.500 --> 39:10.630
While that girl is away,

39:10.630 --> 39:11.810
search the place thoroughly.

39:11.810 --> 39:12.990
You go check outside the yard first.

39:12.990 --> 39:13.940
See if anyone else is there.

39:13.940 --> 39:15.940
-Okay.
-I'll go to the second floor.

39:20.330 --> 39:21.590
No one in the backyard.

39:27.480 --> 39:29.080
No one in the kitchen either.

39:33.540 --> 39:34.990
No one upstairs either.

39:44.260 --> 39:46.310
I shouldn't cause trouble now.

39:46.540 --> 39:48.880
They can't find anything valuable anyway.

39:48.880 --> 39:50.040
Let me tell you,

39:50.120 --> 39:51.820
if we don't find the title deed this time,

39:51.820 --> 39:53.340
we'll lose our jobs.

39:53.360 --> 39:54.420
Look carefully!

39:54.910 --> 39:55.620
Okay.

40:08.070 --> 40:09.920
Mr. Wang, you look quite busy today.

40:09.920 --> 40:11.670
I won't bother you any longer.

40:10.600 --> 40:15.540
[Government]

40:11.940 --> 40:14.630
About the transfer, could you please...

40:14.650 --> 40:15.720
Don't mention it.

40:16.450 --> 40:17.330
Fan Daniu

40:17.460 --> 40:19.190
has already filed the lawsuit.

40:19.390 --> 40:21.010
The hearing will be
in 10 days at the latest.

40:21.010 --> 40:22.630
You'd better be prepared.

40:24.760 --> 40:26.870
[Government]

40:25.310 --> 40:26.640
There's one more thing.

40:27.080 --> 40:28.460
On my wedding day,

40:29.000 --> 40:31.200
please come early for the wedding wine.

40:31.770 --> 40:33.210
Not bad, Changyu.

40:33.410 --> 40:34.640
You move fast.

40:35.220 --> 40:36.280
Congratulations.

40:36.650 --> 40:37.690
I'll definitely be there.

40:37.690 --> 40:45.220
[Qingping County Government Office]

40:38.790 --> 40:41.300
There's one more thing
I need to trouble you with.

40:41.300 --> 40:43.750
My husband's money and travel permit

40:43.780 --> 40:45.590
were all stolen by bandits.

40:45.690 --> 40:47.540
He's marrying into my family soon.

40:47.540 --> 40:49.540
I want to get him a new travel permit.

40:50.230 --> 40:52.290
It coincides with the refugee roundup.

40:52.290 --> 40:53.360
Reissuing a new travel permit

40:53.360 --> 40:54.860
is not an easy task.

40:55.420 --> 40:57.510
But I owe your father a debt of gratitude,

40:57.510 --> 40:59.280
so I will definitely help you.

41:00.290 --> 41:01.420
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

41:01.660 --> 41:03.530
Luckily,
you work at the magistrate's office.

41:03.530 --> 41:04.330
It's nothing.

41:04.390 --> 41:05.720
Consider it a gift.

41:08.460 --> 41:10.260
Right. Look carefully up there.

41:36.930 --> 41:37.500
Found it!

41:38.770 --> 41:39.600
Come.

41:41.670 --> 41:42.290
[Fill Your Belly]

41:42.680 --> 41:43.660
Come!

41:43.970 --> 41:44.450
Look.

41:45.120 --> 41:46.040
That damn girl.

41:46.070 --> 41:47.570
She hid it behind that "Fill Your Belly."

41:47.570 --> 41:49.170
It was so h-hard to find it.

41:48.130 --> 41:55.960
[Fill Your Belly]

41:51.250 --> 41:52.380
We finally found it.

41:52.540 --> 41:53.140
Yes.

41:53.700 --> 41:54.260
Let's go!

41:54.420 --> 41:55.140
Stop.

42:01.770 --> 42:02.900
Why is there a person here?

42:02.900 --> 42:03.530
Didn't you see him?

42:03.530 --> 42:05.060
Didn't you see him just now?

42:10.360 --> 42:11.690
Put down the title deed.

42:13.130 --> 42:13.820
What?

42:14.130 --> 42:15.300
I said,

42:15.910 --> 42:17.540
leave the title deed,

42:18.460 --> 42:20.090
and I'll let you go.

42:22.810 --> 42:23.990
A man with three legs—

42:23.990 --> 42:25.090
he sure is arrogant.

42:25.090 --> 42:26.870
He is a cripple.

42:26.900 --> 42:28.230
You're a cripple.

42:28.300 --> 42:29.780
You can't even stand up.

42:30.180 --> 42:31.380
And you want to fight?

42:32.540 --> 42:35.170
Do you believe
I'll break your good leg too?

42:35.490 --> 42:36.460
Try me.
